beer.beer_description:
On a gathering storm comes a tall handsome man, with dusty black coat and a RED RIGHT HAND...
A, dank, dark, brooding Imperial Red Ale. 
Orange and grapefruit with a touch of pine.
A subtle sweet malt backbone balances perfectly.
